highlights.text: “ハレの日に - Harenohini” by 汐れいら is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 43 spots at #51.
CORTIS has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “GO!” is the highest at #1.
“用背脊唱情歌” by Gareth.T has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 98 days straight.
“Yuck (feat. Ken Carson)” by Young Thug and Ken Carson is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #79.
